        <span class="text-primary font-italic">
            The Player is requested to fill out the company and its representative’s registration form by <span class="font-weight-bold">December 31st, 2024</span>, on <span class="font-weight-bold">Rio2C’s</span> online platform <span class="font-weight-bold">MyRio2C</span> using the link forwarded via e-mail by the event organizers. This registration generates the Player’s profile on the system, which shall be personalized by using a password.
        </span>
    </li>
    <li class="mt-20">
        De <span class="font-weight-bold">1 de fevereiro até 29 de março de 2024</span> todos os executivos que representarão o Player terão acesso aos projetos inscritos em uma área exclusiva na plataforma online <span class="font-weight-bold">MyRio2C</span> do <span class="font-weight-bold">Rio2C</span>. Para avaliar seus projetos, o executivo deverá acessar a plataforma do evento com seu login e senha. |
        <span class="text-primary font-italic">
            Starting from <span class="font-weight-bold">February 1st until March 29th, 2024</span>, all executives (Players) will have access to the submitted projects in <span class="font-weight-bold">MyRio2C</span>, a dedicated area of <span class="font-weight-bold">Rio2C’s</span> online platform. To evaluate your projects, the executive must access the event’s platform with their login and password.
        </span>
    </li>
    <li class="mt-20">
        Os Players terão até o dia <span class="font-weight-bold">29 de março de 2024</span> para selecionar os projetos cujos Participantes desejam se reunir. |
        <span class="text-primary font-italic">
            Players shall have until <span class="font-weight-bold">March 29th, 2024</span>, to mark which projects’ proposing Participants they would like to meet up with.
        </span>
    </li>
</ol>
